                  <td headers="hd_h_hhhs.T.mechanisms_of_drug_action_in_trea_1_1_1_2" valign="middle" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
                    <list list-type="bullet">
                      <list-item>
                        <p>Forms a phenylacetate-glutamine compound via the phenylacetateCoA:glutamine acetyl-transferase reaction&#x000a0;<sup>4</sup></p>
                      </list-item>
                      <list-item>
